message: Priyansh Jadhav (born 31 October 2005) is an Indiansinger, songwriter, record producer, performer and actor. He is known for his singing in Hindi, English, Bengali, Gujarati . He also sung in many Indian languages. He is the little brother Jayneel Jadhav.
